ich is the void located in-between the Earth's atmosphere and any other celestial objects in the milky way. <br />\n<br />\nBased on the circumstance mentioned in the passage, &quot;I&quot; am on Earth and bounded by the gravity of Earth. Therefore, &quot;I&quot; am not travelling in the space. A more accurate way to describe &quot;my&quot; motion would be that &quot;I am travelling in the milky way&quot;. (Who isn't?)"},{"pid":"fb904810c319fdf77d1bdfe4fd5c8b12ffe0920a","tid":2517481,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"邊個reference frame 先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4b282e3a69e23cf27c53b5c066997ffab54a56","tid":2517481,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"要找邏輯謬誤就不是找grammatical mistake 。這論述的問題是：地球的移動應被視為基本，所謂太空旅行應該被視為離開這個基本。沒有定義好太空旅行沒有甚麼好討論。<br />\n<br />\n一切都是定義問題。"},{"pid":"e3aef041d352003cce7ab640e3ffd610657a6d94","tid":2517481,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"420e35e3a5363623f92b8a4f182d731828335742","tid":2517481,"uid":188428,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"橋就我諗，<br />\ncredit就你袋?<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/wa.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"爭就人地抗<br />\n成果就你袋"},{"pid":"5fcd929558e204760cd139a447323d76540e1222","tid":2517481,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c712d022db4377c5f09f483d6fea3c7edf5b6d","tid":2517481,"uid":392351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"Identify and explain any linguistic pitfalls of the following passage: &ldquo;Let me teach you an easy way for travelling in the space. Sit comfortably in the sofa and look through your window. You are now travelling more than 25,000 km a day since the Earth is revolving around the sun!&rdquo;<br />\n<